What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Phosphor Screen Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Phosphor Screen Market

Phosphor screen market is expected to grow at a rate of 3.40% for the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on phosphor screen market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecasted period while providing their impacts on the marketâ€™s growth.

Phosphor screen usually absorbs radiation, electron beam or x-rays and ultraviolet radiation and emits light, based on the wavelength characteristic of the invigorating material. These screens are broadly used in the manufacturing of imaging instruments in various fields such as scientific instruments, consumer electronics, telecommunication devices and medical instruments.

The phosphor screen market is anticipated to witness tremendous growth in the forecast period which is attributed to the increasing usage in manufacturing consumer electronic devices for generating different images. Also the phosphor screens are broadly used in image intensifiers for increasing the strength of the image which is also boosting scope for phosphor screen application and is acting as a key determinant favoring the growth of the market over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. The major factors accountable for the growth of the market are increasing application scope of these phosphor screens in various fields. Beside this, the manufacturing of healthcare equipments is growing due to rising technological advancement in the field of diagnostic instruments. The phosphor screens are used in the manufacturing of instruments such as body scanners and X-Ray imaging. So, the increasing healthcare industry is also helping the market to grow. Furthermore, the presence of storage phosphor screens in the market, which captures latent images produced by ionizing radiation which is also raising the phosphor screen market growth. In addition, phosphor screen is also used in telecommunication equipment such as digital phosphor oscilloscopes, thus flourishing the growth of the phosphor screen market in the above mentioned forecast period. However, the increasing prices of phosphor screen will obstruct the growth of the phosphor screen market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Whereas the lack of infrastructure for large scale production have the potential to challenge the growth of the phosphor screen market in the above mentioned forecast period. The manufacturers are offering phosphor screens with a various decay time according to the various applications which is also lifting the growth of the market.

Furthermore, the expanding research industry, advancements in technology and R&D activities along with high presence of domestic and local players will further offer a variety of growth opportunities for the phosphor screen market.

